---
title: Teriyaki Turkey Rice Bowl with Stir-fried Veggies and Sesame Rice
description: This dish brings the flavour with sesame studded rice, teriyaki hoisin-glazed turkey, and a wok full of Asian veggies. Every bite is packed with flavour and texture - perfect for any day of the week!
